ic_en", "text": "A day of cold:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of intense cold"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A.) ―         -b2-  For the former, see also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SaridN", "text_ar": "صَرِدٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in two places. ―         -b3-  Also, the former,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A high place in mountains;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(AA, L, K;) being the coldest part. (AA, L.)       -A2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SarodN", "text_ar": "صَرْدٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies also"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Pure, unmixed, unadulterated,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "genuine;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, M, L, K;) applied to beverage, (L,) such as is termed"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nabiy*", "text_ar": "نَبِيذ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, L,) and to wine, (L,) and to anything. (M, K.) One says"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ka*ibN SarodN", "text_ar": "كَذِبٌ صَرْدٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "An unmixed lie."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, L.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^uHib~uhu Hub~FA SarodFA", "text_ar": "اُحِبُّهُ حُبًّا صَرْدًا"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I love him with a pure, genuine,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sincere, love."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(AZ, S, L.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jayo$N SarodN", "text_ar": "جَيْشٌ صَرْدٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "An army composed only of the sons of one father"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "ancestor:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(L:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "an army altogether consisting of sons of one's paternal uncle"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of one's relations"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (AO:) or, (M, A, L, K,) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jayo$N SaridN", "text_ar": "جَيْشٌ صَرِدٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, A, L) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SaradN", "text_ar": "صَرَدٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A great army;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K;) (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "an army that appears, from the slowness of its motion, by reason of its great number, to be inanimate."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, A, L.)       -A3-  See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SuradN", "text_ar": "صُرَدٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", near the end."}], "source_refs": ["S", "M", "L", "K", "Lth", "TA", "AO", "A"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}